# Project Framework
- This project uses SolidJS, not React
- Use SolidJS syntax (class instead of className, createSignal instead of useState)
- Use solid-app-router for routing instead of react-router-dom

# Development Guidelines
- Prefer functional style over classes when possible

# Database Access
- SQLite database is stored in OPFS
- Use kysely for database operations
- Database schema is defined in types/schemas.ts
